e.com/news/page/4/|access-date=2022-05-14|language=en-US}}</ref>Halestorm在大多數加拿大的表演中爲樂隊助陣。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Three Days Grace's 2015 Concert & Tour History {{!}} Concert Archives|url=https://www.concertarchives.org/bands/three-days-grace?year=2015|access-date=2022-05-14|work=www.concertarchives.org}}</ref>樂隊於2016年初於歐洲和俄羅斯巡演。<ref>{{Cite web|title=EUROPEAN TOUR EXCLUSIVE TICKET PRE-SALE - Three Days Grace|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311211049/http://threedaysgrace.com/news/just-for-the-community/357623/european-tour-exclusive-ticket-pre-sale|access-date=2022-05-14|date=2018-03-11|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>2016年11月18日，Three Days Grace發行了Phantogram的歌曲“You Don't Get Me High Anymore”的[[翻唱|翻唱]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Three Days Grace - You Don't Get Me High Anymore (Audio) - YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k0gKxgdl7Bw|access-date=2022-05-15|work=www.youtube.com}}</ref> 

