== 影響 ==
樂隊在Billboard Mainstream Rock排行榜上擁有16支榜首的單曲。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Three Days Grace Ties Shinedown for Most Mainstream Rock Airplay No. 1s|url=https://www.billboard.com/pro/three-days-grace-ties-shinedown-most-mainstream-rock-airplay-number-ones/|access-date=2022-05-15|date=2022-02-01|last=Rutherford|first=Kevin|work=Billboard|language=en-US}}</ref>Loudwire將《Animal I Have Become》評為 2012年第45首“21 世紀最佳硬搖滾”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=No. 45: Three Days Grace, 'Animal I Have Become' – Top 21st Century Hard Rock Songs|url=https://loudwire.com/three-days-grace-animal-i-have-become-top-21st-century-hard-rock-songs/|access-date=2022-05-15|last=Raman|first=Liz|work=Loudwire|language=en}}</ref>並在2020年將《Never Too Late》列為 “21 世紀 66 首最佳硬搖滾”之一。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The 66 Best Hard Rock Songs of the 21st Century|url=https://loudwire.com/best-hard-rock-songs-21st-century/|access-date=2022-05-15|last=Staff|first=Loudwire StaffLoudwire|work=Loudwire|language=en}}</ref>《I Hate Everything About You》在2009年的Billboard Decade-End Alternative Songs排行榜上排名第9。<ref>{{Cite journal |date=2009-12-19 |title=Billboard |url=https://worldradiohistory.com/Archive-All-Music/Billboard/00s/2009/BB-.pdf |journal=Decade-End (Hot Alternative Songs) |publisher=Billboard |page=165}}</ref>樂隊前主唱Adam Gontier被認為具有“熱情的聲樂風格、自然沙啞的聲音和充滿焦慮和折磨的q情感”，使他成為被許多青少年和其他生活在艱辛中的人認同的獨特歌手。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Adam Gontier on life after Three Days Grace, the pressure to be a savior, and his band Saint Asonia’s new album|url=https://highwire-magazine.com/2020/11/11/adam-gontier-on-life-after-three-days-grace-the-pressure-to-be-a-savior-and-his-band-saint-asonias-new-album/|access-date=2022-05-15|date=2020-11-11|work=Highwire Magazine|language=en}}</ref>

